00:12:45,539 --> 00:12:46,300
than they are opinions.

289
00:12:46,340 --> 00:12:48,321
But they're not like pure objective facts.

290
00:12:48,341 --> 00:12:50,442
They're very personal kind of facts.

291
00:12:50,863 --> 00:12:53,945
So I find it a good idea to separate those out,

292
00:12:54,025 --> 00:12:55,466
because emotions travel differently

293
00:12:55,506 --> 00:12:56,427
than normal facts do.

294
00:12:57,087 --> 00:12:58,908
So those are three kinds of information, facts, opinions,

295
00:12:58,968 --> 00:12:59,509
and emotions.

296
00:13:00,149 --> 00:13:01,230
And they are about things.

