00:13:17,637 --> 00:13:19,978
But processes are really kind of separate from projects,

305
00:13:20,018 --> 00:13:21,458
the way you do things, how you do things.

306
00:13:22,098 --> 00:13:23,259
And then the third one is people,

307
00:13:24,579 --> 00:13:26,200
because people are doing these projects.

308
00:13:26,841 --> 00:13:28,043
OK, well that's a thing.

309
00:13:28,103 --> 00:13:29,084
Maybe you can break that out.

310
00:13:29,384 --> 00:13:31,567
You have facts, opinions, and emotions about projects,

311
00:13:31,687 --> 00:13:32,609
processes, and people.

312
00:13:33,443 --> 00:13:34,404
Well, OK, that's something.

