00:13:36,145 --> 00:13:36,445
I don't know.

315
00:13:36,485 --> 00:13:37,245
It's not perfect.

316
00:13:37,585 --> 00:13:40,266
But going back to the spreadsheet and going back to

317
00:13:40,286 --> 00:13:43,548
the big thing, kind of made the six columns, and started to

318
00:13:43,588 --> 00:13:44,348
kind of check it off.

319
00:13:44,388 --> 00:13:48,970
And it's like, yeah, new studio policy, that's a fact

