00:40:49,804 --> 00:40:51,124
Now, of course, there's lots of kinds of noise.

980
00:40:51,184 --> 00:40:52,904
There's a lot of kinds.

981
00:40:53,124 --> 00:40:55,385
There's certainly the noise in your head.

982
00:40:55,605 --> 00:40:57,205
You're worried about some personal problem,

983
00:40:57,565 --> 00:41:00,346
or oh my god, oh my god, I'm going to get fired, whatever.

984
00:41:00,706 --> 00:41:02,106
Noise in your head is not going to help you.

985
00:41:02,306 --> 00:41:04,967
So you want to find ways to reduce the noise in your head.

986
00:41:05,567 --> 00:41:07,787
There's actual noise in the office.

987
00:41:08,867 --> 00:41:10,108
That can block information flow.

988
00:41:10,128 --> 00:41:11,988
Anyone who's ever been to a party at the minute gallery

989
00:41:12,368 --> 00:41:13,008
knows about that.

990
00:41:13,748 --> 00:41:15,429
Hey, man, I haven't seen you for a year.

